{
  "stem": "12868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've been always with humor, you know, and everybody laugh whenever-- even-- even the Germans laugh sometimes what I did to them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used make sometimes-- one German, what he came into work every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was Christmastime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he knew I do a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted to make him a doll from wood for his grandson.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he wanted to give this for him a present.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he come in the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took a piece of wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he gave me a piece of bread every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he had sometimes a piece of meat or something like this from home, he give me-- you know, nobody to see.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or sometimes he wrapped up in a piece of paper a-- a-- a-- a piece of chicken or something like this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he looked-- nobody, nobody Germans to see it what they're doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he threw this is in the wood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he say, go, pick up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Pick-- go, pick up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I said, come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in the wood, I open up, I see a piece of chicken.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I sit down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when I eat this-- what I did for him, a doll.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I keep doing this for him for weeks, only to get time more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, I didn't-- I didn't do the other work hard, only this what I did for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When I make a doll, I make up how much I can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- and this, what he-- he give me sometimes a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Every day, he bring me something else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But that's what I am lucky with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But later on, I got-- have to-- near to the liberation, I got very sick.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
